
If you don't want to use the virtual machine, here are the two workspaces required to run the Tiago Robot.
 - tiago_ws: all tiago-related packages
 - ros2_ws: contains the ros-control packages
 link: https://liveunibo-my.sharepoint.com/personal/alessio_caporali_unibo_it/_layouts/15/onedrive.aspx?id=%2Fpersonal%2Falessio%5Fcaporali%5Funibo%5Fit%2FDocuments%2F0%5FTEACH%2FAMR%2Flab%5Fpackages&ga=1

It is important to keep these workspaces separated since otherwise it is difficult to compile everything.

First, build the ros2_ws and add the corresponding setup.bash to the bashrc.
Then, proceed to build the tiago_ws.

ATTENTION: before colcon building these two workspaces, you should have ROS2 Humble installed and also install all of the following:

sudo apt update
sudo apt install ros-humble-test-msgs

sudo apt update
sudo apt install ros-humble-ros-gz-sim

sudo apt update
sudo apt install python3-pytest

sudo apt install ros-humble-twist-mux

sudo apt update
sudo apt install ros-humble-launch-param-builder

sudo apt update
sudo apt install ros-humble-moveit-configs-utils

sudo apt update
sudo apt install ros-humble-moveit

per ora ho installato questi!

sudo apt update && sudo apt install -y \
  ros-humble-play-motion2 \
  ros-humble-play-motion2-msgs \
  ros-humble-moveit \
  ros-humble-moveit-ros-perception \
  ros-humble-moveit-ros-planning-interface \
  ros-humble-controller-manager \
  ros-humble-joint-state-broadcaster \
  ros-humble-joint-trajectory-controller \
  ros-humble-diff-drive-controller \
  ros-humble-force-torque-sensor-broadcaster \
  ros-humble-twist-mux \
  ros-humble-twist-mux-msgs \
  ros-humble-tiago-description \
  ros-humble-tiago-moveit-config \
  ros-humble-tiago-gazebo \
  python3-yaml

pip install PyYAML
pip install jinja2 typeguard

pip install PyQt5
pip install PySide2
pip install python_qt_binding
pip install PyQt5-sip

sudo apt install ros-humble-pmb2-description
sudo apt install ros-humble-pmb2-gazebo

sudo apt install python3-scipy

sudo apt install python3-pykdl

sudo apt-get install ros-humble-aruco-ros

